item.title: Did the Best Denver Broncos Team Actually Win a Super Bowl?
item.description: The Denver Broncos have been consistently bad over the last six seasons, in part due to hall of fame quarterback Peyton Manning retiring. However, they are still a highly decorated team, having won three Super Bowls (tied for 7th most) and having appeared in eight of them (tied for 3rd most). Many argue as to whether Manning or John Elway was the best Broncos quarterback of all time, but which team was the best?
